<br />But from preservation point of view iNES sucks big time and I'm guessing this is the reason why Marty made his proposal. I pesonally would like to see a more descriptive format intended for preservation of the games/box-art/manuals for future generations when all carts have bit-rots and all box-art/manuals are gone.

		

