<br />
<br />Until there is a netlist mapper format any custom mapper will be just as ambiguous when described in text or a number.  How would the emulator be able to add support by itself using the xml description of a board that does chrram banking and unrom type prg banking with different data bits?  If you require a person to add that to the emulator its no different than calling those specs mapper #x.

		

