<br />Agreed++. My opinion is to <strong>accept</strong> new ideas, even if this one (XML) looks controversial. I still believe that UNIF <strong>is</strong> the best choice, though it needs to be more popular between emulator authors and the community (read: players). So, the users will make the choice. 
